WEBVTT

00:07:57.184 --> 00:08:00.912
now doctors can find 91%
of the high-risk regions,

00:08:00.936 --> 00:08:02.663
simply by changing the colors.

00:08:02.687 --> 00:08:05.966
(Applause)

00:08:05.990 --> 00:08:09.033
